                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18411025-2684-offence-1 t18411025-cd-124"></join>25th of October</rs>, 4 pieces of carpet, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18411025-name-802" type="victimName">
